OL,3,CHow will the new golf ball rule affect
OL,4,Cthe game for pros and amateurs?
OL,6,FGolf might be about to get harder for
OL,7,Fprofessionals and amateurs alike as
OL,8,Fthe sport's governing bodies announced
OL,9,Fa major change that seeks to curb how
OL,10,Ffar a golfer can hit a ball for
OL,11,Feveryone from Tiger Woods to a weekend
OL,12,Fhacker.
OL,14,FIn a significant step for the game,
OL,15,Fthe United States Golf Association
OL,16,F(USGA) and the Royal and Ancient Golf
OL,17,FClub of St Andrews (R&A) announced
OL,18,Fballs will be slowed in a bid to rein
OL,19,Fin increasingly long drives.
